Flubber
via found it on the ground

Flubber


In two separate bowls combine:

A: 	1.5 c white glue
	2 c water

	Mix with a fork - can add a few drops of food coloring

in second bowl:

B:	4 tsp borax
	1 1/3 c water

	Mix with a fork

Pour B over A - DO NOT MIX

Let stand a few minutes
Lift out and knead
Store in a baggie